{
  "texts": [
    "At the same time, a version of Hoang's BARTABSA model that used the original sets of categories for classification was tested to demonstrate the effectiveness of dividing categories into two sets of classes.",
    "This paper refers to the modified method as BARTABSA(split).",
    "The BARTABSA(split) model outperformed the BARTABSA (Hoang).",
    "Table 8 shows a significant performance gap between the BARTABSA(split) and Extract-Classify-ACOS models.",
    "However, the BARTABSA(split) model performs worse than the previous model Extract-Classify-ACOS on the EA &IO sub-task, with a decrease of about 4% in REST-ACOS as shown in Table 8."
  ]
}